spec: agent-core.ai-docs/v1
namespace: Command
fqcn: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Command"
updatedAt: 2026-04-19
description: Symfony console commands for operational management of the agent loop.
files[2]{file,type,summary}:
  AgentLoopResumeStaleRunsCommand.php,final class,This command identifies and resumes agent runs that have become stale or stuck in an intermediate state. It coordinates with storage and locking mechanisms to safely transition these runs back into an active execution loop.
  AgentLoopHealthCommand.php,final class,This class implements a Symfony console command to monitor and report the health status of an agent loop. It utilizes a provided configuration array to determine operational parameters and outputs diagnostic information to the console.